&lt;p&gt;This role will require you travelling across North East Derbyshire as part of a wider, integrated team, providing holistic care to patients in their own homes.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;It is expected you will have experience working in either a health or social care setting. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;A good standard of English is required, along with good communication skills.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a clinical employee it will be your responsibility to ensure that your behaviour and values reflect those set out in the DCHS Way.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Phil Parkes Integrated Community Team Leadl philip.parkes@nhs.net 07721 879764&lt;/p&gt;
